Package: ggQC
Type: Package
Title: Scaleable Quality Control
Version: 0.0.0.8650
Author: Kenith Grey
Maintainer: Kenith Grey <kenithgrey@r-bar.net>
Description: Scaleable Quality Control makes determinating quality control
  limits and ploting scaleable for single variable as well as multi-parameter processes. A 
  range of methods are available for constuctiong QC charts in ggplot2 including the 
  standard XmR and XbarR charts. Additional methods are avalable for robust analysis of 
  noisy data using xMedian-rMedian calculations and plotting capabilites.   
Depends: R (>= 2.10)
License: GPL-3 | file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Suggests: testthat,
    gridExtra
RoxygenNote: 6.0.0
Imports: ggplot2,
    reshape2,
    stats,
    plyr
